    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Setuptools_scm Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Setuptools_scm</application> package is used to extract
Python package versions from git or hg metadata instead of declaring them.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
      <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&setuptools_scm-download-http;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&setuptools_scm-download-ftp;"/>
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Soma de verificao MD5: &setuptools_scm-md5sum;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tamanho da transferncia: &setuptools_scm-size;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Espao em disco estimado exigido: &setuptools_scm-buildsize;
          </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>
            Tempo de construo estimado: &setuptools_scm-time;
          </para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Dependncias de Setuptools_scm</bridgehead>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect5">Exigida</bridgehead>
      <para role="required">
        <xref linkend="packaging"/> and <xref linkend="typing_extensions"/>
      </para>

      <bridgehead renderas="sect5">Optional (for testing)</bridgehead>
      <para role="optional">
        <xref linkend="git"/>, <xref linkend="mercurial"/>, and <xref
linkend="pytest"/>
      </para>

    </sect3>

    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Setuptools_scm</title>

    <para>Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user setuptools_scm</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      The installation can be tested with <command>pytest</command>. A few tests
may fail if your <application>git</application> configuration is not the one
expected by the test suite.
    </para>

    </sect3>

